code: @Test public void testClientFactoryUpdated() throws Exception {     Endpoint endpoint = context.getEndpoint("google-drive://drive-files/list?clientFactory=#myAuth").     assertTrue(endpoint instanceof GoogleDriveEndpoint).     assertTrue(((GoogleDriveEndpoint) endpoint).getClientFactory() instanceof MyClientFactory). }
@Override protected JndiRegistry createRegistry() throws Exception {     JndiRegistry registry = super.createRegistry().     registry.bind("myAuth", new MyClientFactory()).     return registry. }

@Override protected RouteBuilder createRouteBuilder() throws Exception {     return new RouteBuilder() {          public void configure() {             from("google-drive://drive-files/list?clientFactory=#myAuth").to("mock:result").         }     }. }
